[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/pluck">Pluck</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/pluck">Pluck</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user pecks the foe. If the foe is holding a Berry, the user plucks it and gains its effect.</p>